@node Doc.ToolTypes "IceIQle, Doc: ToolTypes"
ICON TOOLTYPES     (Alphabetized)
--------------

When setting up for the first time, the important ToolTypes to set up
are EDITOR, PHRASEDIR, HEADER, and TAGLINE for generating proper
output.

Any item that is only applicable when used in conjunction with the
IceBBS communications software is indicated with [IceBBS Only],
similarly for AmiQWK.

   @{" APPENDLINES " link ToolTypes.AppendLines}    (Integer)
   @{" CLEANUP " link ToolTypes.CleanUp}        (BOOLEAN)    [IceBBS and AmiQWK Only]
   @{" EDITOR " link ToolTypes.Editor}         (String)
   @{" EXCLUDEINFO " link ToolTypes.ExcludeInfo}    (Multiple string)
   @{" EXCLUDENUM " link ToolTypes.ExcludeNum}     (Integer  -  Default: 8)
   @{" HEADER " link ToolTypes.Header}         (String)    [IceBBS and AmiQWK only]
   @{" HEADER2 " link ToolTypes.Header2}        (String)    [IceBBS and AmiQWK Only]
   @{" HEADERMAIL " link ToolTypes.HeaderMail}     (String)    [IceBBS Only]
   @{" OMIT " link ToolTypes.Omit}           (Multiple String)
   @{" PHRASEDIR " link ToolTypes.PhraseDir}      (String)
   @{" QUOTING " link ToolTypes.Quoting}        (Switch  -  Default: ON)
   @{" TAGLINE " link ToolTypes.TagLine}        (String)
   @{" TAGMAIL " link ToolTypes.TagMail}        (String)    [IceBBS Only]
   @{" WORDWRAP " link ToolTypes.WordWrap}       (Integer  -  default: 0 / OFF)    [IceBBS/AmiQWK]
   @{" WRAPMARGIN " link ToolTypes.WordWrap}     (Integer  -  default: 15)         [IceBBS/AmiQWK]

@endnode

